508
00:42:58,760 --> 00:43:00,040
Mas não disseste.

509
00:43:01,800 --> 00:43:02,880
E sabes porquê?

510
00:43:07,880 --> 00:43:09,640
Porque és uma falhada

511
00:43:10,080 --> 00:43:12,520
